Dear Micha, dear friends,
<span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5;">thank you for making aware the context of the different variants of the [[unpartei/WorldAnthem|WorldAnthem]][[http://google.com/search?q=WorldAnthem|➜°]].</span>

That rises the question: Is it [[unpartei/CreativeCommons|CreativeCommons]][[http://google.com/search?q=CreativeCommons|➜°]] or a mere Commercial for realizing particular interests.

Can a copyrighted [[unpartei/WorldAnthem|WorldAnthem]][[http://google.com/search?q=WorldAnthem|➜°]] be a [[unpartei/TrueWorldAnthem|TrueWorldAnthem]][[http://google.com/search?q=TrueWorldAnthem|➜°]] in the following sense?

A true [[unpartei/WorldAnthem|WorldAnthem]][[http://google.com/search?q=WorldAnthem|➜°]] belongs to all humanity, everyone should be free to
+ use it without having to pay for it
<span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5;">+ make derivative works of it and</span>
<span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5;">+ vote for it </span>

<span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5;">That leads to a dynamical concept of a stream of [[unpartei/WorldAnthems|WorldAnthems]][[http://google.com/search?q=WorldAnthems|➜°]] that mirrors the planetarian thoughts, feelings and hope for a common worthwhile future of the planet.</span>

So let's search for a [[unpartei/CreativeCommonsWorldAnthem|CreativeCommonsWorldAnthem]][[http://google.com/search?q=CreativeCommonsWorldAnthem|➜°]].

